          "text": "All 4 seasons have their best sides... If you like rising nature, flowers, then May. If you like warmer weather and the beach, then maybe July. If you like autumn colours, then September-October. If you like winter and Christmas, then December-January... The best time to travel with a rental car is May - September when the roads are safe, no ice. June, July are nice because then we have no darkness at nights  - like polar day.",
